com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.configuration

Class ClusterPrecheckResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.configuration.ClusterPrecheckResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.vmware.vapi.bindings.StaticStructure, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Structure, java.io.Serializable

    public final class ClusterPrecheckResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.StaticStructure
    The PrecheckResult class contains properties that describe precheck status of applying the desired document to a group of hosts. This class was added in vSphere API 8.0.1.0.
